    "name": "FOOD-ITEM Copy",
    "description": "## Food Item API\n\nThis collection covers the core endpoints for managing **food items** in the application. It provides the essential operations to interact with the food item resource exposed at `http://localhost:3000/api/food`.\n\n### Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|--------|----------|-------------|\n| `POST` | `/api/food` | **Create** a new food item |\n| `GET` | `/api/food` | **Retrieve** all food items |\n\n### Usage\n\nUse the **Create** request to add new food items to the system, and the **Get items** request to fetch the full list of available food items. These endpoints form the foundation of the food item management workflow.",
